25|$|A <b>forced</b> <b>disappearance</b> (or {{enforced}} disappearance) {{occurs when}} a person is secretly abducted or imprisoned by a state or political organization or by a third party with the authorization, support, or acquiescence of a state or political organization, followed by a refusal to acknowledge the person's fate and whereabouts, with the intent of placing the victim outside the protection of the law.|$|E
